text: Vasilați is a commune in Călăraşi County, Muntenia, Romania. It is composed of three villages: Nuci, Popești and Vasilați. Gălbinași village belonged to Vasilați until 2005, when it was split off to form Gălbinași Commune. ==References== Category:Communes in Călărași County Category:Localities in Muntenia
title: Vasilați
